OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInflation measure shake-up 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Famid Jack Monroe row       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Food poverty campaigner and chef Jack  
OL,6, Monroe is claiming victory after       
OL,7, statistics chiefs pledged to revise how
OL,8, they measure the cost of living.       
OL,10,FMs Monroe had complained that everyday 
OL,11,Fessentials were going up in price by   
OL,12,Fmore than the official inflation rate, 
OL,13,Fhitting poorer people hardest.         
OL,15,FBut she said the official way inflation
OL,16,Fis calculated failed to reflect this.  
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, the Office for National  
OL,19,FStatistics admitted that "one inflation
OL,20,Frate doesn't fit all".                 
